snippet.title: Industries of Titan Combat Trailer
snippet.description:
Industries of Titan is an industrial city building sim/strategy game, set on Saturn's moon Titan.

Wishlist now on Steam!: http://store.steampowered.com/app/427940/Industries_of_Titan/

Developed by Brace Yourself Games, creators of Crypt of the NecroDancer!

Website: http://industriesoftitan.com
Twitter: http://twitter.com/IndustriesGame
Facebook: http://facebook.com/IndustriesOfTitan

Art by Sir Carma and Nick Gunn: https://twitter.com/sir_carma & https://twitter.com/Gunn3D
Music by Danny Baranowsky: https://twitter.com/dannyBstyle
Trailer by Marlon Wiebe: http://mwiebe.com/
Sound by Power Up Audio: https://twitter.com/PowerUpAudio
Actors, in order of appearance: David Attar, Elspeth Eastman
